<br>
The new line of spells are nice and I'd like to see what they add for the ones that can get them but for a person like me I have very little chance of getting one and I'm ok with that because I choose to be where I am....if I wanted high end I would chase after it...I'm not mad at verant for that, its my choise to be where I am.<br>
<br>
Now for the lower level casters out there its very VERY tuff to level up unless your in a guild or have friend that will group with you or power level up a bit so I'm hoping this statement was a start to work with them as well because soon there will come a time when the only casters you will see are the ones that are at Raid level...I'm seeing that now, WAY more melees out there now then a few years ago...much like Bards, they were everywhere not more then a maybe a year..year and a half ago...now?...I can't say I have seen many at all and if i did they were on a raid somewhere...I'm not saying the lack of Bards is because there weak....only a fool would think that but they are rare because there a tuff class to play the players needs to nurture the class to get it right...not too far off from casters but we need more then &quot;nurtureing&quot;..we need some real help and I'm hoping that this is that &quot;help&quot;.<br>
<br>
<br>
If Verant is starting to truly pay attention to the problems some of us casters are having, I can only hope that they see it form all levels, not just 55 plus because even though that is were most of us are heaing it wouldn't matter if we can get there because were too weak in the lower leves to get into a group....Raid level increase is great but worthless if there is no one that gets that high to use it because they give up at the lower levels for lack of groups taking them in.<br>
<br>
